<br>
The Wizard Alternate Advancement ability Improved Familiar has been upgraded on the Test Server.<br>
Currently this ability only gives the Wizard an extra 25 to all resists and See Invisible.<br>
<br>
The revised version on Test, in addition to the resists and see invisible components, now increases the Wizards mana by 200, adds 6 extra mana regeneration per tick and reduces the chance of Wizards spells fizzling or being resisted.<br>
<br>
Note: This is of course only on the Test server and may change before going live. <br>
------------------------------------------------------------<br>
<br>
