<br>
Wezloc<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/urhionsligo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>rhionsligo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Arch Mage</span><br>  Posts: 511<br> <font color=#333333>(5/4/02 11:01:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=196.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/starofdavid.gif width=36 height=37></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_mad.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: More Wizard improvements and still nada for Mages! errrr</span><hr size=1> OK...valid points wezloc, but I dont see why we should all go hyperventalating just because wizards got an improvement...   If anything it means we have to summon them less rods for them to nuke with. <p><img src="http://www.lehigh.edu/~dsf3/EQ/rhionsligo.jpg" align="center"><br>
